Articles.Content:
Since 0.25 I just have only some kind of contracts, for example I've never seen test part contracts like in 0.24, just 1 rescue mission so far, the number of contracts seem poor (2,3 per time) not like in 0.24 and continuous repeatly the same after completation. I get very often "Plant a flag on the Mun" or "Get Science from Kerbin orbit", no more test a part neiter from modded parts.

I've tried several intallations with and without mods. I use KSP 32bit.
